0.name: Commands
0.description: Displays Bot Commands and syntax. Alternative to pb help

1.name: Hello
1.description: Takes a second to solve some linear algebra and traverse some optic fibres only to come say Hello to you :)

2.name: Help
2.description: Displays Discord standard bot help with commands, very similar to this.

3.name: Inspire
3.description: Gets you an inspirational quote from the Interwebs.

4.name: Movie
4.description: Gets you details and rating for the movie you've mentioned.

5.name: Ping
5.description: Says Pong. It might do some calculus and fetch you my server ping as well.

6.name: Rick Roll
6.description: Rickrolls the mentioned user anonymously. Or tells you to get a life. Which one is it? Who knows.

7.name: RPS
7.description: Plays Rock Paper Scissors with you. I don't cheat, I promise. To those of you who didn't understand why I said that, learn to code, I'm sure a job would help.

8.name: Joke
8.description: Delivers a joke from the internet. Dark/Programming/Pun/Spooky go into the category, or nothing, upto you.

9.name: Chuck Norris Joke
9.description: Delivers a Chuck Norris joke from the internet, if you're into that. To be honest, I don't find these funny, prove me wrong.

10.name: Yo Mama Joke
10.description: Delivers a joke from yo mama, aka you.

11.name: Vote Kick
11.description: Vote Kick's a member from your private channel. Stress on **Vote**.

12.name: Private Invite
12.description: Invites the mentioned to your private channel. You can kick them out later, it's chill.

13.name: Match
13.description: Calculates your compatibility with the mentioned person.

15.name: Status
15.description: Retreives the bot server status from a monitoring service.

16.name: Support
16.description: Use for bot support, to request for a feature or to report a bug.

17.name: Clear
17.description: Clears the specified number of messages. If unspecified clears just the previous message.

18.name: Define
18.description: Retrieves all available definitions for the specified term.

19.name: Urban
19.description: Retreives the top defintion from Urban Dictionary for the specified term or something random.
